<item>
            <title>[LU-5297] osp_sync_thread can&apos;t handle invalid record gracefully</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5297</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;osp_sync_process_queues() now assumes all records to be processed are not corrupted, it&apos;s lack of error handling code for invalid records.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One solution could be regarding the invalid record as committed and skipping  processing on it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
