                            <comment id="116308" author="gerrit" created="Mon, 25 May 2015 07:03:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Emoly Liu (emoly.liu@intel.com) uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/14925&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/14925&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5297&quot; title=&quot;osp_sync_thread can&amp;#39;t handle invalid record gracefully&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5297&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5297&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; osp: decrease opd_syn_changes for an invalid record&lt;br/&gt;
